<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 12 at 7:33PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Snow and blowing snow will impact Southern Beaverhead County
through this evening...
Periods of snow and northwesterly winds gusting up to 30 mph will
impact the southern portion of Beaverhead County for the remainder
of this evening. Anyone traveling interstate 15 from Lima to
Monida Pass should expect slippery roads and reduced visibility
below one half mile at times due to snow and blowing snow. Use
caution if traveling or delay travel if possible.</description>
